<p>In Sweden we have a public funding program open for everyone. The idea is that a group of people can come together and study or learn and improve a skill, and in return receive help to achieve their goals. One kind of help they offer is monthly grants to reimburse costs for materials. I'm now going to apply to create such a group, with the purpose to study the fear of life, its antidote, and to look for new ways to talk about it. We are obviously going to need study materials found in the JustOneLook web store!</p>
