<p>Thank you, JaJa83! There is a lot of traffic to our website from all over. Here in the forum we have people from everywhere. Just today we welcomed a new member who lives in Kazakhstan!</p><p>It should not be hard to find other people in your city or country who are here in the forum.</p><p>How about this? Forum members interested in connecting with other forum members who have not yet introduced themselves, go ahead and make a brief posting telling us all how you found Just One Look, where you live, etc. And let us know if you are interested in meeting with other lookers in person.</p><p>Also, don't forget the chat feature, which is new in the forum. There is a speech bubble next to each member's name. If they are online, there is a green dot next to their name. If you think someone might be in your area, you can send them a message and ask!</p><p>If you want to gather a group of people in your area to talk about Just One Look and find ways to support the project, post an invitation here!</p>
