<p>I had the intention to process and trade with certain herbs and got everything ready (website, logo, equipment etc.). I borrowed some money to start up and import the herbs but almost all my goods were seized by the customs, except Chaga. They said they now implement a new interpretation of a law with a very strange, even ridiculous argumentation but I won't go into that now. So I lost all my money but the structure (Logo, webshop, registred company etc.) is still in place so I could revive it for this purpose now. I can give as much as possible to the foundation but there are some expenses that need to be covered (webspace, label printing, packaging, tax etc.). Check for the price of 3kg, I will see if I can raise the money (it's still early in the month). We should use the chat function from now on I think.</p>
