<div class="forum-post-template-post">
<p>I got a response regarding my grant application and unfortunately this work falls under their definition of "treatment" and is therefore not eligible for their support. So back to the drawing board!</p><p><span class="forum-post-bold">Let's keep the ideas coming!!</span> <img src="smilies/smile.png" alt="smily"></p><p>By the way Carla, I cannot create comments on other posts in this sub forum. It might be a bug if you didn't mean it that way?</p>
</div><!-- class="forum-post-template-post" -->
</div><!-- class="forum-post-template-container" -->







