<p>JaJa, we just found out about a site in Germany that is for fundraising campaigns. They seem really good and their processing rates are lower than the ones in the US. Maybe you guys who live in Germany could get together and set up a fundraising campaign to support The River Ganga Foundation. If you come up with a really good text and good pictures. that could work. <a href="https://www.betterplace.org/en">https://www.betterplace.org/en</a></p>
